reviewText: Dinner for schmucks is my third favorite movie. Under apriciated and deep.

Two great movies about love from different angles and each is equally successful, laughable, . Steve Carrel is most ridiculous in the most hilarious Dinner.... and still gets at least one wet cheek.....and yet... melancholy and serious in Crazy....both movies contain excellent story lines, and great supporting casts in the genre of each... here again.. I have little to write.. except GET IT!
This is a great double disk set. So funny !!!!! Both movies get better every time you watch it !!
2 great movies by a great actor. Plus you can't beat 2 movies for the price of 1. Would receommend to everyone.

Crazy Stupid Love is a great, fun movie and Ryan Gosling and Emma Stone have incredible chemistry.

Dinner for Schmucks is just fun.
Love these movies. Everyone should add them to their movie collection.
Great for a night of Steve Carell!
Only one DVD was inside. Was missing dinner with the smucks
Crazy Stupid Love is an excellent movie with an all star cast and great twist. Dinner for Schmucks is a good Steve Carrel movie that just make this pakage even better at this price.
Love both of these movies, great value
